    "text": "Note, the LABEL function should not be confused with the label type of widget. There are 2 default types available in the add widget menu, both of which are shown to the right. They are the same except for size and font-size. Label widgets are 'textareas', which is now seen mostly as a disadvantage. The only advantage labels have over other widget types is the 'editable' property, which if set to true, allows a player to change the text without using a JSON editor.  ",
